Bafin to Raise Budget, Add Employees, Handelsblatt Reports

-- B y   N i k l a s   M a g n u s s o n
-- 
2011-06-28T06:41:10Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-28/bafin-to-raise-budget-add-employees-handelsblatt-reports.html
German financial regulator Bafin
plans to raise its budget to 160 million euros ($228 million)
and increase the number of employees by 12 percent to 2,200
people this year,  Handelsblatt  newspaper reported today, citing
Michael Sell, head of internal administration at Bafin.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Niklas Magnusson in Hamburg at 
 nmagnusson1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Angela Cullen at 
